##  Architecture at a Glance

Letâ€™s revisit the high-level diagram from earlier:

[Clinic Users] ---> Route53 ---> AWS WAF & Shield ---> OpenMRS (EC2 in Private Subnet)
|
Amazon RDS (MySQL)
